    <item>
      <title>特朗普在拉斯维加斯集会上重申“不征收小费税”的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-26/trump-reiterates-no-tax-on-tips-promise-in-vegas-rally-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统在内华达州拉斯维加斯的胜利集会上重申了他在竞选中承诺取消小费税的承诺。他表示，这项提议将影响大约 400 万依赖小费收入的工人，其中 70 万是单身母亲。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-26/trump-reiterates-no-tax-on-tips-promise-in-vegas-rally-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 14:33:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街最大的希望是特朗普在移民问题上保持克制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/wall-street-s-big-hope-is-trump-pulls-his-punches-on-immigration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的移民政策开始成型，可能对美国企业的增长和收益产生毁灭性的影响。投资者似乎还没有太过不安——主要是因为他们不相信他会全面实施他的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/wall-street-s-big-hope-is-trump-pulls-his-punches-on-immigration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>货币波动将消灭新兴市场套利交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/currency-volatility-set-to-wipe-out-emerging-market-carry-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普政府的关税威胁和美元进一步上涨的前景挤压了回报，新兴市场投资者对套利交易变得越来越谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/currency-volatility-set-to-wipe-out-emerging-market-carry-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股 15 万亿美元的涨势取决于高风险的盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/tech-s-15-trillion-rally-hinges-on-high-stakes-earnings-stretch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者正进入又一个关键的大型科技公司盈利周期，这些公司的股价接近历史高点，估值也过高。这次的一个关键区别是：这些公司的利润增长预计将达到近两年来的最慢速度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/tech-s-15-trillion-rally-hinges-on-high-stakes-earnings-stretch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊福普民意调查显示马克龙支持率跌至历史最低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/macron-s-approval-rating-drops-to-record-low-in-ifop-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据伊福普研究所为《星期日报》开展的一项民意调查，埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的支持率已跌至 2017 年就任法国总统以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/macron-s-approval-rating-drops-to-record-low-in-ifop-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 12:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>驱逐出境的经济学</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-26/economics-of-deportations-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统认为移民执法是促进家政工人发展的一种方式，但经济状况却表明并非如此。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-26/economics-of-deportations-video</guid>
