      <title>中国加大指数投资力度 力图重振市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/china-boosts-index-investments-in-latest-bid-to-revive-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国宣布了推动指数投资产品发展的新举措，这是中国在面临动荡的外部经济环境之际为支撑低迷的股市所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/china-boosts-index-investments-in-latest-bid-to-revive-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 10:28:47 GMT</pubDate>
